dc_title_s: Preliminary sewer survey: City of Jeffersonville & suburbs, County of Clark, State of Indiana
dc_description_s: Shows 1884 and 1937 high water lines and floodwall. Blueprint. Includes diagram of Louisville and Portland Canal gages showing high water on various dates. 'April 1946.' 'Plate no. 1.' Scale approximately 1:6,000. Compiled by J.W. Bruner; drawn by Chester F. Stemler.
